---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="TuEmpresa - Servicios">
  <!-- Hero Section de Servicios -->
  <section class="relative py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-indigo-700 text-white overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Elementos decorativos de fondo -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-20">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-blue-400 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-80 h-80 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">Nuestros Servicios</h1>
        <p class="text-xl opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
          Ofrecemos soluciones digitales completas para ayudar a tu empresa a crecer y destacar en el entorno digital actual. Nuestro enfoque personalizado garantiza resultados excepcionales.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Curva decorativa inferior -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full overflow-hidden">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1200 120" preserveAspectRatio="none" class="w-full h-16 text-white">
        <path d="M321.39,56.44c58-10.79,114.16-30.13,172-41.86,82.39-16.72,168.19-17.73,250.45-.39C823.78,31,906.67,72,985.66,92.83c70.05,18.48,146.53,26.09,214.34,3V120H0V0C0,0,31,6.27,96.48,70.28c74.58,72.26,88.27,50.19,224.91-13.84Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Navegación de servicios -->
  <section class="py-8 bg-white border-b sticky top-20 z-30">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex flex-nowrap overflow-x-auto md:justify-center space-x-4 pb-2 md:pb-0 services-nav">
        <a href="#diseno-web" class="inline-block px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-gray-700 font-medium hover:bg-blue-50 hover:text-blue-600 whitespace-nowrap transition-colors">Diseño Web</a>
        <a href="#desarrollo-web" class="inline-block px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-gray-700 font-medium hover:bg-blue-50 hover:text-blue-600 whitespace-nowrap transition-colors">Desarrollo Web</a>
        <a href="#marketing-digital" class="inline-block px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-gray-700 font-medium hover:bg-blue-50 hover:text-blue-600 whitespace-nowrap transition-colors">Marketing Digital</a>
        <a href="#consultoria" class="inline-block px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-gray-700 font-medium hover:bg-blue-50 hover:text-blue-600 whitespace-nowrap transition-colors">Consultoría</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Introducción a Servicios -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="md:col-span-2">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">Soluciones digitales completas</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            En TuEmpresa diseñamos soluciones digitales a medida que impulsan el crecimiento de tu negocio. Nuestro enfoque se centra en entender tus necesidades específicas para ofrecerte las herramientas y estrategias más adecuadas.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Combinamos creatividad, tecnología y estrategia para crear experiencias digitales que conectan con tus usuarios y generan resultados tangibles. Desde el diseño hasta la implementación, te acompañamos en cada paso del proceso.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Soluciones a medida</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Tecnología de punta</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Equipo experto</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Atención personalizada</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Resultados medibles</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Soporte continuo</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:flex items-center justify-center hidden">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-blue-100 rounded-full opacity-70 transform rotate-45"></div>
            <div class="relative bg-white p-2 rounded-full shadow-lg">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-32 w-32 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Servicio 1: Diseño Web -->
  <section id="diseno-web" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 flex-shrink-0 mr-4 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Diseño Web</h2>
          </div>
          
          <div class="w-20 h-1.5 bg-blue-600 mb-8 rounded-full"></div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 text-lg">
            Creamos diseños atractivos y funcionales que representan la identidad de tu marca y ofrecen una experiencia excepcional al usuario. Nuestro enfoque centrado en el usuario garantiza sitios web que no solo lucen bien, sino que también convierten visitantes en clientes.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm mb-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">¿Qué incluye nuestro servicio?</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span><span class="font-medium">Diseño responsivo</span> - Optimizado para todos los dispositivos y tamaños de pantalla</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span><span class="font-medium">UX/UI intuitivo</span> - Interfaces amigables y fáciles de navegar</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span><span class="font-medium">Optimización de velocidad</span> - Sitios rápidos que mejoran SEO y conversión</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span><span class="font-medium">Identidad visual</span> - Diseño alineado con tu marca y objetivos</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors font-medium shadow-md group">
            <span>Solicitar información</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:order-first relative">
          <div class="relative z-10 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
            <img 
              src="/img/services/web-design.jpg" 
              alt="Diseño Web" 
              class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
              onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='/api/placeholder/600/400'; this.alt='Imagen de diseño web'"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Elemento decorativo detrás de la imagen -->
          <div class="absolute -z-10 w-full h-full bg-blue-100 rounded-lg top-8 -left-8"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Servicio 2: Desarrollo Web -->
  <section id="desarrollo-web" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 flex-shrink-0 mr-4 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Desarrollo Web</h2>
          </div>
          
          <div class="w-20 h-1.5 bg-blue-600 mb-8 rounded-full"></div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 text-lg">
            Creamos sitios web y aplicaciones personalizadas con las últimas tecnologías para ofrecer soluciones robustas y escalables. Nuestro enfoque técnico garantiza productos de alta calidad que satisfacen las necesidades específicas de tu negocio.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm mb-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">¿Qué incluye nuestro servicio?</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span><span class="font-medium">Desarrollo frontend</span> - React, Vue.js, Angular y otras tecnologías modernas</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span><span class="font-medium">Desarrollo backend</span> - Node.js, Python, PHP y soluciones personalizadas</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span><span class="font-medium">E-commerce</span> - Tiendas online con pasarelas de pago integradas</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span><span class="font-medium">CMS</span> - Sistemas de gestión de contenidos personalizados</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors font-medium shadow-md group">
            <span>Solicitar información</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="relative z-10 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
            <img 
              src="/img/services/web-development.jpg" 
              alt="Desarrollo Web" 
              class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
              onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='/api/placeholder/600/400'; this.alt='Imagen de desarrollo web'"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Elemento decorativo detrás de la imagen -->
          <div class="absolute -z-10 w-full h-full bg-blue-100 rounded-lg top-8 right-8"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Servicio 3: Marketing Digital -->
  <section id="marketing-digital" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 flex-shrink-0 mr-4 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 3.055A9.001 9.001 0 1020.945 13H11V3.055z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.488 9H15V3.512A9.025 9.025 0 0120.488 9z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Marketing Digital</h2>
          </div>
          
          <div class="w-20 h-1.5 bg-blue-600 mb-8 rounded-full"></div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 text-lg">
            Desarrollamos estrategias efectivas para aumentar tu presencia online, atraer clientes potenciales y aumentar tus conversiones. Nuestro enfoque basado en datos garantiza campañas optimizadas que generan un retorno medible de tu inversión.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm mb-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800">¿Qué incluye nuestro servicio?</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
